Optional third-party tools (not bundled or redistributed)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

trufflehog (https://github.com/trufflesecurity/trufflehog)
    License: AGPL-3.0
    Use:     When a `trufflehog` binary is present on the user's PATH,
             leakferret invokes it as a separate process for fallback
             verification of providers it does not natively cover.

    leakferret does NOT bundle, ship, download, modify, or link trufflehog,
    and contains none of its source code. trufflehog is installed
    independently by the user, and leakferret communicates with it only at
    arm's length via subprocess invocation. Removing trufflehog from PATH
    disables the fallback with no other effect.
